title: Bobby Tests How Well Jessie James Decker & Eric Decker Know Each Other + Raymundo Is Celebrating His First Father's Day
itunes:title: Bobby Tests How Well Jessie James Decker & Eric Decker Know Each Other + Raymundo Is Celebrating His First Father's Day
description:
Jessie James Decker stops by the studio with her husband Eric. Bobby puts them to the test to see how much they know about one another. Producer Raymundo talks about celebrating his first Father's Day this year. Also, Bobby and Eddie have a new Bobby Bones & The Raging Idiots song!
